column.name: Id
column.Comment: Primary key for the API log entry

column.name: ApiKeyId
column.Comment: Foreign key reference to the API key used for the request

column.name: SessionId
column.Comment: Session identifier for tracking user sessions

column.name: RequestPath
column.Comment: The API endpoint path that was requested

column.name: StatusCode
column.Comment: HTTP status code returned by the API

column.name: StatusMessage
column.Comment: HTTP status message or custom response message

column.name: RequestMethod
column.Comment: HTTP method used for the request (GET, POST, PUT, PATCH, DELETE, etc.)

column.name: SourceIp
column.Comment: Source IP address of the client making the request

column.name: ResponseLatency
column.Comment: Response time in milliseconds for performance monitoring

column.name: Id
column.Comment: Primary key for audit log entry

column.name: Action
column.Comment: Description of the action performed (GDPR sensitive)

column.name: Category
column.Comment: Category classification for the audit action

column.name: NewValue
column.Comment: New value after the change (JSON format)

column.name: OldValue
column.Comment: Previous value before the change (JSON format)

column.name: ModifiedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the action was performed

column.name: TenantId
column.Comment: Foreign key to the tenant where the action occurred

column.name: UserId
column.Comment: Foreign key to the user who performed the action

column.name: Id
column.Comment: Primary key for country region using ULID format

column.name: Name
column.Comment: Name of the region within the country (e.g., Syddanmark, Midtjylland)

column.name: CountryId
column.Comment: Foreign key to the country this region belongs to

column.name: Id
column.Comment: Primary key for email address

column.name: Address
column.Comment: Email address following RFC 5321 standards

column.name: UserId
column.Comment: Foreign key to the user who owns this email

column.name: CustomerId
column.Comment: Optional foreign key to associated customer

column.name: TenantId
column.Comment: Optional foreign key to associated tenant

column.name: Id
column.Comment: Primary key for integration

column.name: OwnerId
column.Comment: Foreign key to the user who owns this integration

column.name: Name
column.Comment: Friendly name for the integration

column.name: ServiceName
column.Comment: Name of the third-party service (e.g., Stripe, SendGrid, Twilio)

column.name: Description
column.Comment: Optional description of the integration purpose

column.name: ApiKeySecretReference
column.Comment: Reference to the securely stored API key

column.name: CreatedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the integration was created

column.name: LastUpdatedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the integration was last updated

column.name: Id
column.Comment: Unique identifier for the payment provider

column.name: Name
column.Comment: Name of the payment provider (e.g., Stripe, PayPal, Square)

column.name: Description
column.Comment: Optional description of the payment provider and its capabilities

column.name: IsActive
column.Comment: Indicates if this payment provider is currently active and available for use

column.name: CreatedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the payment provider was created

column.name: LastUpdatedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the payment provider was last updated

column.name: Name
column.Comment: The permission name (e.g., 'read:users', 'write:documents')

column.name: Description
column.Comment: Optional description of what this permission allows

column.name: CreatedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the permission was created

column.name: LastUpdatedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the permission was last modified

column.name: Name
column.Comment: The role name (e.g., Administrator, User, Manager)

column.name: Description
column.Comment: Optional description of the role's purpose and permissions

column.name: CreatedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the role was created

column.name: LastUpdatedAt
column.Comment: Timestamp when the role was last modified

column.name: Id

column.name: Name

column.name: Description

column.name: Code

column.name: Status
